{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_12_02",
  "title": "成宮すず",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――劇団★見の公演が近づいたある日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お願いがありますの\n実はお父様とお母様が今回の舞台を観たがっていまして",
      "startTime": 6.616108259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "相変わらず熱心で優しいご両親だな\n分かった、関係者席を用意してもらおう",
      "startTime": 16.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ありがとうございます\nお父様とお母様も喜んでくれますわ",
      "startTime": 22.9132856051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "今から本番が楽しみですわね……なんと言っても\n今回こそアリス役を見せられるんですから",
      "startTime": 32.1799510001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "はっ……違うんですのよ！？\n今のは言葉の綾と言いますか……",
      "startTime": 39.2466143608,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2653.385639199996,
          "startTime": 41.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、すまない、念のため関係者席の件、公演関係者に\n連絡を入れていたところだ。問題なく用意出来そうだよ",
      "startTime": 46.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ええと、それで聞き逃してしまったんだが……\nもう一度言ってくれるか？",
      "startTime": 55.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "ほっ……いいんですの\n全く関係のない独り言でしたから",
      "startTime": 61.6624641418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうか？　なら、いいんだが……。そうだ\nそういえば今度、月ストの仕事が星見市であったよな",
      "startTime": 69.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "その時にでも案内も兼ねてご両親に挨拶に行こう\nすずのスケジュールも合わせておくよ",
      "startTime": 77.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　私の家に行くんですの！？\nええと……だ、大丈夫……ですわよね？",
      "startTime": 84.1510604817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、俺は大丈夫だが\nもしかして都合が悪いのか……？",
      "startTime": 92.2333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、せっかくの{user}さんのご厚意\nですから！　い、行きましょう行きましょう！",
      "startTime": 98.0695296765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後、成宮家にて",
      "startTime": 102.603428471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narudining-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "narudining-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.9034249106
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narudining-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "narudining-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.9034249106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "さ！　お父様とお母様に挨拶も出来ましたし\nそろそろ帰りましょう！",
      "startTime": 108.802859958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "も、もう行くのか？　まだ着いて五分だぞ\n最低限の挨拶しか出来てないのに……",
      "startTime": 114.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narudining-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "narudining-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.1472334344
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "こ、今回の劇は絶対に成功させたいんですの！\n出来る限り練習に時間を割かせてくださいまし！",
      "startTime": 122.1183013122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narudining-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "narudining-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.2783236305
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことだったら仕方ない\nでは、すみませんが本日はここで……",
      "startTime": 129.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "え？　最後に見せたい物があるんですか？\nこのDVDは一体……？",
      "startTime": 137.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narudining-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "narudining-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.8250665784
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "んなっ！？　お父様、お母様ぁ！？\nそれは私のアリスの劇が録画されたDVDでは！？",
      "startTime": 143.7317124527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "なんだ、ちゃんと撮ってくれていたんじゃないか\n録画してなかったっていうのは勘違いだったみたいだな",
      "startTime": 152.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narudining-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "narudining-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.5113025149
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そ、そうみたい、ですわね……\nですが、その、お父様、お母様……",
      "startTime": 160.8082885584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "では、ご厚意に甘えさせていただきます\nさっそく昔のすずの演技を観てみようか",
      "startTime": 168.3833661198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narudining-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "narudining-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.706699415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "ダメですわ！！\n絶対にダメですわよ！？",
      "startTime": 173.3282884439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narudining-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "narudining-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.2040689747
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いや……え、ええと……そう！\n確か今、プレイヤーが故障しているはず！",
      "startTime": 181.8282884439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narudining-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "narudining-00-noon",
      "startTime": 185.1434457104
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "むやみやたらに触ったら感電しますわよ！？\n危険ですわ！　こっちによこしてくださいまし！",
      "startTime": 188.5282772542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そんな馬鹿な……動くぞ、ほら\n壊れていないみたいで良かった",
      "startTime": 196.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_switch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2273.6096420999843,
          "startTime": 194.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narudining-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "narudining-00-noon",
      "startTime": 198.901787309
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、ええっと、そうですわ！\n心霊現象が映っていますのよ！　観たら呪われますわ！",
      "startTime": 203.8703378202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "「昨日観たがそんなシーンはない」と\nお父さんとお母さんが言っているが……",
      "startTime": 213.4666748047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narudining-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "narudining-00-noon",
      "startTime": 215.9509511274
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "昨日も観たんですの！？\nそ、それどころか週一！？",
      "startTime": 218.2826312226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narudining-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "narudining-00-noon",
      "startTime": 228.6159645559
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "お父様、お母様、それほど私のことを……\nいえ、違いますわ、そうじゃなくて……",
      "startTime": 228.6159645559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narudining-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "narudining-00-noon",
      "startTime": 232.4833218378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_02-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "ええと、ええと～～……\nじゃあ、じゃあ…………うぅ～……",
      "startTime": 238.0159543833,
      "sfxList": [
        {
